  "title": "Warehouse Assistant #80834",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Material Handling Equipment Supplier</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Warehouse Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: East – Ubi (Walking distance from MRT to the company)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon-Fri: 8.30am-6pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 2800 + AWS</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Receive, inspect, and document incoming materials and deliveries</li><li>Accurately pack and prepare outgoing orders for timely dispatch</li><li>Assist with organizing, labeling, and storing inventory in designated areas</li><li>Support spare parts production, including latex component fabrication from mixing and production to assembly according to Standard Operating Procedures</li><li>Maintain a clean, safe, and orderly work environment</li><li>Operate warehouse equipment such as pallet jacks, trolleys, or forklifts</li><li>Ensure compliance with all safety, quality, and hygiene standards</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. N level</li><li>Min.1 year of working experience in related field</li><li>Able to handle manual lifting</li><li>Have forklift license is a plus</li><li>Basic mechanical aptitude or experience in component/parts assembly would be an advantage</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80834 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
